{
  "texts": [
    "The number of training epochs is set to 20 with a mini-batch size of 32 due to limited GPU memory.",
    "The model is implemented under HuggingFace's Transformers library (Shen et al., 2023) and trained on eight NVIDIA V100 GPUs using DeepSpeed Zero stage 3 (Yao et al., 2023).",
    "Overall performance.",
    "As shown in Table 1, the supervised fine-tuning Qwen, or Qwen-SFT, surpassed GPT-3.5 on both datasets.",
    "It also achieved comparable performance to GPT-4 on CN100 and exceeded GPT-4 on EN100."
  ]
}